{"tid":163890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]前妻要高額生活費　川漢攬女投河雙亡","createTime":"2017-03-20T10:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T12:31:28.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"862e945304c29f80748eb3b1dfc7f49759ea7991","tid":163890,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170319/bkncn-20170319090021094-0319_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170319%2Fbkncn-20170319090021094-0319_05011_001.html&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3e8ae849\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170319/bkncn-20170319090021094-0319_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170319/photo/bkncn-20170319090021094-0319_05011_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170319%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170319090021094-0319_05011_001_02b.jpg&h=de8e5edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川眉山市仁壽縣前日發生倫常慘劇，一名男子抱着年僅一歲多的女兒跳河輕生，雙雙溺亡。知情者稱，該男子與妻子離婚後，女兒跟隨前妻生活，惟因前妻逼其每月給孩子5000元人民幣的生活費，最終他無奈下攬女跳河自盡。<br />\n<br />\n從現場短片所見，該對父女遺體被打撈上岸後，兩人仍緊緊擁在一起。後經現場民眾將該對父女分離後，溺斃男子雙臂仍呈現抱緊狀態，而現場有一名疑為男死者的前妻，跪在女童屍體旁痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n當地公安內部文件顯示，於事發當日，陳姓男死者的楊姓前妻已因瑣事，毆打陳男母親，其後楊女更聯同母親圍毆陳母。其中楊女母親已被行政拘留10天。惟陳姓男死者自盡的確切原因，官方未有公布。<br />\n<br />\n好事成雙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff84a8890a68603dcd2e7f91300d2fda4c06c60","tid":163890,"uid":57952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"女人累人"},{"pid":"551c73b2e19eb18c02783ece7e1cef5728a10778","tid":163890,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"窮人_ _ _"}]}